metaText.title: 24th Ps New V. 46 2 Over,2voices. WHG.069
metaText.history: donated by Mrs W.R.Kettlewell to VWML,Apr 1927.
metaText.author: Oxfordshire - Bampton
metaText.notes:
See notes on WHG068. Key signature indistinct,
but "in C" written at start of system.
The asterisked bars are marked as insertions;
i.e. a ^ symbol and miniature bars below the
staves. The 2nd voice bar is |a2zd| in the MS!
The last note of section 1 is G2 in voice 1,
E4 in voice 2. I have edited these to G3 and
E3 respectively, and added the final rest.
The bar "£" is |dzz2| in the MS.
